The mountainous regions of Bansko, Borovec, Pamprovo and Vitosa are the most preferred, as well as on the Albena beaches, the "Golden Coast", the "Coast of the Sun", the old Sozopol and Nesebar, but increasingly more people seek properties also in the surroundings of Kavarna and Balchik.
